# S2-2: User Profile Page

Build a public profile page for each registered user, showing their display name, bio, and participation history. Owners can edit their own profile inline. The Header gets a "Sign in with Google" link for unauthenticated users.

All backend endpoints are already live from S2-1:
- `GET /api/users/:id` — public profile + participation history
- `PATCH /api/users/me` — update display name + bio (JWT)
- `GET /api/auth/me` — get current logged-in user (JWT)

