## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
```bash
cd client && npm test
```

### Manual
1. Run `cd server && npm run dev` + `cd client && npm run dev`
2. Navigate to `http://localhost:5173` — Header shows "Sign in"
3. Click "Sign in" → Google OAuth → redirected back → Header shows display name
4. Navigate to `/users/:your-id` — see your profile with bio + logs
5. Click Edit → update bio → save → verify update persists
6. Open a different user's profile (logged out) — Edit button must NOT appear
